tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE iris_scan_results (
    iris_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    matching_score FLOAT,
    match_status TEXT,
    scan_date TIMESTAMP,
    scan_location TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE IrisScans (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  scan_result FLOAT,
  scan_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Users (user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  access_level INT,
  joined_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE MatchResults (result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  scan_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  match_status BOOLEAN,
  match_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE ScanHistory (history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  scan_id INT,
  scan_status VARCHAR(100),
  scanned_by VARCHAR(50),
  scan_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE matches (
    match_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    scan_id_1 UUID,
    scan_id_2 UUID,
    match_score FLOAT,
    match_result BOOLEAN
);
